;/i&gt; Half damage.&lt;/p&gt;]] (⚔)(➶) <b>Bone Javelin</b> (weapon) ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Attack:</i> Melee 1 or Ranged 5 (one creature); [[/roll 1d20+7[ vs. AC]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔)(➶) &lt;b&gt;Bone Javelin&lt;/b&gt; (weapon) ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Melee 1 or Ranged 5 (one creature); &lt;u&gt;+7 vs. AC&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;]]</p><p><i>Hit:</i> [[/roll 2d6 #&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔)(➶) &lt;b&gt;Bone Javelin&lt;/b&gt; (weapon) ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 2d6 damage.&lt;/p&gt;]] <7> damage.</p><p><i>Miss:</i> Half damage.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Effective Recruitment&lt;/b&gt; (charm) ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect:&lt;/i&gt; The recruiter chooses one adjacent enemy who can hear and understand the recruiter. Until the end of the recruiter’s next turn, all melee and ranged attacks made against the recruiter instead target the chosen enemy. Additionally, while this effect is active, the recruiter deals an extra 2d6 damage with attacks against the chosen enemy.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Effective Recruitment</b> (charm) ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Effect:</i> The recruiter chooses one adjacent enemy who can hear and understand the recruiter. Until the end of the recruiter’s next turn, all melee and ranged attacks made against the recruiter instead target the chosen enemy. Additionally, while this effect is active, the recruiter deals an extra [[/roll 2d6 #&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Effective Recruitment&lt;/b&gt; (charm) ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect:&lt;/i&gt; The recruiter chooses one adjacent enemy who can hear and understand the recruiter. Until the end of the recruiter’s next turn, all melee and ranged attacks made against the recruiter instead target the chosen enemy. Additionally, while this effect is active, the recruiter deals an extra 2d6 damage with attacks against the chosen enemy.&lt;/p&gt;]] <7> damage with attacks against the chosen enemy.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Minor</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Psionic Mask&lt;/b&gt; (illusion) ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect:&lt;/i&gt; The recruiter creates a psionic illusion that allows the recruiter to appear as any Medium humanoid until it uses psionic mask again or until it drops to 0 hit points. To create an illusion of a specific individual’s form, the recruiter must have seen that individual. Other creatures can make a DC 20 Insight check to discern the presence of the psionic illusion.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Psionic Mask</b> (illusion) ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Effect:</i> The recruiter creates a psionic illusion that allows the recruiter to appear as any Medium humanoid until it uses psionic mask again or until it drops to 0 hit points. To create an illusion of a specific individual’s form, the recruiter must have seen that individual. Other creatures can make a DC 20 Insight check to discern the presence of the psionic illusion.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Triggered</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Scatter&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Trigger:&lt;/i&gt; The cultist is hit by a close or area attack that also includes one of its allies as a target.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect (Immediate Interrupt):&lt;/i&gt; The cultist shifts up to its speed. If the cultist ends this shift in a space outside of the area of the triggering attack, the attack does not hit the cultist.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Scatter</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> The cultist is hit by a close or area attack that also includes one of its allies as a target.</p><p><i>Effect (Immediate Interrupt):</i> The cultist shifts up to its speed. If the cultist ends this shift in a space outside of the area of the triggering attack, the attack does not hit the cultist.</p></tr></td></table>",
